\[\det\Bigl{(}\lambda\mathbf{I}-\mathbf{L}_{1}(a)\Bigr{)}=\det\Bigl{(}\lambda \mathbf{I}-\mathbf{L}_{1}(b)\Bigr{)}=(\lambda-3)^{2}(\lambda-1)^{2}(\lambda^{ 3}-9\lambda^{2}+21\lambda-7) \tag{50}\]

